description:
N°13 Release, 久岐忍 - Kuki Shinobu from Genshin Impact - 原神.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Examples Image is now active, Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

I just wanted a Better Quality & More Flexible LORA of Shinobu, so i created it.

This Lora is trained on 314+ Images with Good quality, I sorted everything manually, Only picked the best possible. (SFW + NFSW)

AnimeFullFinalPrunedFP16 used, so he work with the majority of Anime Model, you can see in examples images. (Abyss Model + 7th Corneo's Heaven's Model + YesMix Model + MeinaMixV8 Model.)

This Lora have 2 Version: N°1: Default Skin: Default Kuki Shinobu Skin With & Without Mask. N°2: Kuki Shinobu with Long hair Straight in Miko Skin.

About Trigger Words & Prompts: KShinobuV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples image.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Work perfectly at Weight 1, Best result: 0.7-1

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).
